twitch_info.title: Kamilia 3 - Speedrun to Boss Rush in 2:33:28
twitch_info.description:
Decent run, going all the way to boss rush was completely unplanned which is why I don't have splits for Stage 4 (and Stage 4 was pretty much unpracticed for weeks). Definitely planning to improve this run.
This was during a Stage 2 race with CasualCrap, Stinkycheeseone890, and Thwink2.
YouTube Upload: [http://youtu.be/hxmR04srpt4](http://youtu.be/hxmR04srpt4)
